726740f-a.title: Queens: Furmanville Avenue - 77th Street
726740f-a.text:
Furmanville Ave., north side, in 77th Street. This house does
not appear in the 1929 OQueens Atlas. The probable owners of this
house were J. Bedell, 1852-1850, G.H. Sichman, 1873 to 1891, and
J. Boening in 1891. One 2ork, a florist, was the occupant in 1923.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
